metadata.name: TEMPORAL DISARRAY
metadata.description: TEMPORAL DISARRAY embodies the essence of THE SURVIVAL OF AN IDEA collection, representing the resilience of a creative idea and its journey through the chaos of time. The piece showcases the interplay between order and disorder, capturing the beauty in the imperfections and unpredictability of life. As the first installment in the collection, TEMPORAL DISARRAY sets the tone for the exploration of the enduring power of the human spirit in the face of adversity.
